fields.query:
SELECT
  "LOCATION_ID", "NAME"
FROM
  "LOCATION"

WHERE
  "LOCATION_ID" IN (
    SELECT
      "LOCATION_ID"
    FROM
      "GROUP_LOCATION"
    WHERE
      "GROUP_ID" = [GROUP_ID]
    )
    OR
    [ROLE_ID] NOT IN (6, 7, 1105)
ORDER BY "NAME"

fields.name: Leitbehörde
fields.query:
SELECT DISTINCT
  "AUTHORITY"."AUTHORITY_ID",
  "AUTHORITY"."NAME"
FROM
  "AUTHORITY"
LEFT JOIN
  "GROUP_LOCATION" ON (
  "GROUP_LOCATION"."GROUP_ID" = [GROUP_ID]
)
LEFT JOIN
  "GROUP" ON (
  "GROUP"."GROUP_ID" = [GROUP_ID]
)
LEFT JOIN
  "AUTHORITY_LOCATION" ON (
    "AUTHORITY"."AUTHORITY_ID" = "AUTHORITY_LOCATION"."AUTHORITY_ID"
  )
 
JOIN
  "AUTHORITY_AUTHORITY_TYPE" "AAT" ON (
    "AUTHORITY"."AUTHORITY_ID" = "AAT"."AUTHORITY_ID"
  )
JOIN
  "AUTHORITY_TYPE" "AT" ON (
    "AAT"."AUTHORITY_TYPE_ID" = "AT"."AUTHORITY_TYPE_ID"
  )
LEFT JOIN
  "FORM_GROUP_FORM" "FGF" ON (
    "FGF"."FORM_ID" = [URL_FORM_ID]
  )

WHERE (

  (
    "GROUP_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" = "AUTHORITY_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID"
    AND
    (
      ("FGF"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 30 AND "AT"."TAG" = 'BG')
      OR
      ("FGF"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 141 AND "AT"."TAG" = 'NP')
    )
  )
  OR
  -- HACK: If the Group is Bundestelle set Leitbehoerde to BAV
  (
	"GROUP"."GROUP_ID" = 1028
	 AND
	"AUTHORITY"."AUTHORITY_ID" = 75
  )
  OR
  (
    "GROUP_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" IS NULL
    AND
	NOT "GROUP"."GROUP_ID" = 1028
  )

)
ORDER BY "AUTHORITY"."NAME"

fields.query:
SELECT  DISTINCT
  "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID",
  "DOSSIERNR"."ANSWER" as "DOSSIER_NR",
  "FORM"."NAME"        as "FORM",
  "LOCATION"."NAME"    as "COMMUNITY",
  "USER"."USERNAME"        AS "USER",
  "APPLICANT_VIEW"."APPLICANT",
  (SELECT STRING_AGG("NAME", ', ' ORDER BY "NAME")
    FROM "INTENTIONS" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AS "INTENT",
  (SELECT STRING_AGG("NAME", ', ' ORDER BY "NAME")
    FROM "SANCTION"
    JOIN "SERVICE" ON (
      "SANCTION"."SERVICE_ID" = "SERVICE"."SERVICE_ID"
    )
    WHERE "SANCTION"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID"
  ) AS "SANCTION",
  CASE
    WHEN "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."ANSWER" IS NOT NULL THEN "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."ANSWER"
    WHEN "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."ANSWER" IS NOT NULL THEN "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."ANSWER"
    WHEN "ANSWER_STREET_247"."ANSWER" IS NOT NULL THEN "ANSWER_STREET_247"."ANSWER"
  END AS "STREET",
  "GET_INST_STATE_NAME_BY_ID"("INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID") AS "STATE",
  "INSTANCE_STATE_DESCRIPTION"."DESCRIPTION"    AS "STATE_DESCRIPTION"
FROM "INSTANCE"
LEFT JOIN "APPLICANT_VIEW" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "APPLICANT_VIEW"."INSTANCE_ID"
)
JOIN "INSTANCE_LOCATION" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."INSTANCE_ID"
)
JOIN "LOCATION" ON (
    "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" = "LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID"
)
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER"  "DOSSIERNR" ON (
    "DOSSIERNR"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "DOSSIERNR"."QUESTION_ID" = 6
    AND
    "DOSSIERNR"."CHAPTER_ID" = 2
    AND
    "DOSSIERNR"."ITEM" = 1
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER" "ANSWER_INTENT" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_INTENT"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "ANSWER_INTENT"."QUESTION_ID" = 97
    AND
    "ANSWER_INTENT"."CHAPTER_ID" = 21
    AND
    "ANSWER_INTENT"."ITEM" = 1
  )

LEFT JOIN "ANSWER_STREET_BG" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."INSTANCE_ID"
  )

LEFT JOIN "ANSWER_STREET_NP" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."INSTANCE_ID"
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER_STREET_247" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_STREET_247"."INSTANCE_ID"
  )
join "FORM" ON (
  "INSTANCE"."FORM_ID" = "FORM"."FORM_ID"
)
JOIN "USER" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."USER_ID" = "USER"."USER_ID"
)
LEFT JOIN "INSTANCE_STATE_DESCRIPTION" ON (
    "INSTANCE_STATE_DESCRIPTION"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID"
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER"  "PARCEL_NR" ON (
  "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "PARCEL_NR"."INSTANCE_ID"
  AND "PARCEL_NR"."QUESTION_ID" = 91 AND "PARCEL_NR"."CHAPTER_ID" = 21 AND "PARCEL_NR"."ITEM" = 1
  )
JOIN "FORM_GROUP_FORM" ON (
  "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_ID" = "INSTANCE"."FORM_ID"
)
left JOIN "GROUP_LOCATION" ON (
     "GROUP_LOCATION"."GROUP_ID" = [GROUP_ID]
  )
LEFT JOIN "CIRCULATION" ON (
  "CIRCULATION"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID"
)

LEFT JOIN "ACTIVATION" ON (
  "ACTIVATION"."CIRCULATION_ID" = "CIRCULATION"."CIRCULATION_ID"
)
LEFT JOIN "SANCTION" ON (
  "SANCTION"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID"
)
WHERE "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID" != 28
AND (
    ([ROLE_ID] = 3 AND ("FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 30 OR "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_ID" = 293))
  OR
    ([ROLE_ID] IN (7, 6, 1104) AND "GROUP_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" = "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID")
  OR
    ("FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_ID" != 293
      AND (
          ([ROLE_ID] = 1061 AND "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 141)
        OR
          ([ROLE_ID] = 1101 AND "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 241)
        OR
          ([ROLE_ID] = 1105 AND "GROUP_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" = "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" AND "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 253)
        OR
          ([ROLE_ID] NOT IN (3, 1061, 6, 7, 1105, 1104))
	  )
	)
)

select  distinct
  "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID",
  "DOSSIERNR"."ANSWER" as "DOSSIER_NR",
  "FORM"."NAME"        as "FORM",
  "LOCATION"."NAME"    as "COMMUNITY",
  "USER"."USERNAME"        AS "USER",
  CASE WHEN
      "ANSWER_COMPANY"."ANSWER" IS NOT NULL 
    THEN "ANSWER_COMPANY"."ANSWER"
    ELSE "ANSWER_APPLICANT"."ANSWER"
  END AS "PETITION",
  (SELECT STRING_AGG("NAME", ', ' ORDER BY "NAME") 
    FROM "INTENTIONS" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AS "INTENT",
  CASE
    WHEN "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."ANSWER" IS NOT NULL THEN "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."ANSWER"
    WHEN "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."ANSWER" IS NOT NULL THEN "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."ANSWER"
  END AS "STREET",
  GET_STATE_NAME_BY_ID("INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID") AS "STATE",
  "INSTANCE_STATE_DESCRIPTION"."DESCRIPTION"    AS "STATE_DESCRIPTION"


  
FROM "INSTANCE"

JOIN "INSTANCE_LOCATION" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."INSTANCE_ID"
)

JOIN "LOCATION" ON (
    "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" = "LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID"
)

LEFT JOIN "ANSWER"  "DOSSIERNR" ON (
    "DOSSIERNR"."INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "DOSSIERNR"."QUESTION_ID" = 6
    AND
    "DOSSIERNR"."CHAPTER_ID" = 2
    AND
    "DOSSIERNR"."ITEM" = 1
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER" "ANSWER_APPLICANT" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_APPLICANT"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "ANSWER_APPLICANT"."QUESTION_ID" = 23
    AND
    "ANSWER_APPLICANT"."CHAPTER_ID" = 1
    AND
    "ANSWER_APPLICANT"."ITEM" = 1
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER" "ANSWER_INTENT" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_INTENT"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "ANSWER_INTENT"."QUESTION_ID" = 97
    AND
    "ANSWER_INTENT"."CHAPTER_ID" = 21
    AND
    "ANSWER_INTENT"."ITEM" = 1
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER" "ANSWER_COMPANY" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_COMPANY"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "ANSWER_COMPANY"."QUESTION_ID" = 221
    AND
    "ANSWER_COMPANY"."CHAPTER_ID" = 1
    AND
    "ANSWER_COMPANY"."ITEM" = 1
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER" "ANSWER_STREET_BG" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."QUESTION_ID" = 93
    AND
    "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."CHAPTER_ID" = 21
    AND
    "ANSWER_STREET_BG"."ITEM" = 1
  )
LEFT JOIN "ANSWER" "ANSWER_STREET_NP" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."INSTANCE_ID"
    AND
    "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."QUESTION_ID" = 93
    AND
    "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."CHAPTER_ID" = 101
    AND
    "ANSWER_STREET_NP"."ITEM" = 1
  )



join "FORM" ON (
  "INSTANCE"."FORM_ID" = "FORM"."FORM_ID"
)

JOIN "USER" ON (
    "INSTANCE"."USER_ID" = "USER"."USER_ID"
)

LEFT JOIN "INSTANCE_STATE_DESCRIPTION" ON (
    "INSTANCE_STATE_DESCRIPTION"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_STATE_ID"
  )

LEFT JOIN "ANSWER"  "PARCEL_NR" ON ( 
  "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" = "PARCEL_NR"."INSTANCE_ID" AND "PARCEL_NR"."QUESTION_ID" = 91 AND "PARCEL_NR"."CHAPTER_ID" = 21 AND "PARCEL_NR"."ITEM" = 1
  )

JOIN "FORM_GROUP_FORM" ON (
  "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_ID" = "INSTANCE"."FORM_ID"
)

JOIN
  "GROUP_LOCATION" ON (
     "GROUP_LOCATION"."GROUP_ID" = [GROUP_ID]
  )

WHERE
  (([ROLE_ID] = 3 AND "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 30)
  OR
  ([ROLE_ID] = 1061 AND "FORM_GROUP_FORM"."FORM_GROUP_ID" = 141)
  OR (
    ([ROLE_ID] = 7 OR [ROLE_ID] = 6) AND 
    "GROUP_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID" = "INSTANCE_LOCATION"."LOCATION_ID"
  )
  OR
  ([ROLE_ID] NOT IN (3, 1061, 7, 6)))

fields.query:
"INSTANCE"."CREATION_DATE" >= (TO_DATE('01-01-2017', 'DD-MM-YY')) AND (
  ? = 'nachforderung' AND (
    13 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    14 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'pendente_publikationen' AND (
    1 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    15 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'einsprachen' AND (
    21 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    15 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'dossier_zum_freischalten' AND (
    1 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    16 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'erteilte_baubewilligungen' AND (
    47 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    55 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'abgelaufene_baubewilligungen' AND (
    71 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    55 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    1 IN (SELECT CASE WHEN "WORKFLOW_DATE" < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY"
        WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID" AND "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" = 71)
  )

  OR ? = 'schnurgeruestabnahmen_pendent' AND (
    55 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    56 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'baustellen_in_betrieb' AND (
    55 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    67 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'endabnahmen_pendent' AND (
    67 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") AND
    59 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  )

  OR ? = 'rechtsmittelverfahren' AND (
    (
      48 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") OR
      50 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") OR
      52 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID") OR
      63 IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
    )
    AND
    54 NOT IN (SELECT "WORKFLOW_ITEM_ID" FROM "WORKFLOW_ENTRY" WHERE "INSTANCE_ID" = "INSTANCE"."INSTANCE_ID")
  ))
